00:24:19,375 --> 00:24:22,500
♪ ROCKING, GO RAISING HELL ♪
♪ ROLLING, GO RAISING HELL ♪

400
00:24:25,625 --> 00:24:28,708
♪ FASTER, GO RAISING HELL ♪
♪ HARDER, GO RAISING HELL ♪

401
00:24:28,791 --> 00:24:31,250
♪ WE'RE GONNA YELL ♪
♪ AND STORM SPREAD THIS FIRE ♪

402
00:24:31,333 --> 00:24:33,333
- HE'S NOT AFRAID OF ANYTHING,
IS HE?

403
00:24:33,416 --> 00:24:35,500
DUDE'S RIDIN' ME CLOSE ENOUGH
THE SPRAY MUST BE TOTALLY

404
00:24:35,583 --> 00:24:37,291
BLOCKING HIS HEADLIGHTS.

405
00:24:37,375 --> 00:24:39,000
THAT'S WHY I CHOSE TO LEAD.

406
00:24:39,083 --> 00:24:41,250
LOW VISIBILITY'S NOT MY BAG.

407
00:24:41,333 --> 00:24:43,333
BETWEEN THE RAIN AND THE DARK,
THERE'S NO WAY IN HELL

408
00:24:43,416 --> 00:24:44,958
YOU CAN SEE WHERE YOU'RE GOIN'.

409
00:24:45,041 --> 00:24:47,583
AND THE CLOSER YOU GET,
THE WORSE IT'S GONNA BE.

410
00:24:50,875 --> 00:24:52,291
- ( revving )

411
00:24:55,625 --> 00:24:57,208
- ♪ RAISING HELL ♪

412
00:24:59,375 --> 00:25:01,708
- HE'S GAINING ON ME? BUT HOW?

413
00:25:01,791 --> 00:25:04,416
HOW COULD ANYONE FOLLOW
MY LINE IN THESE CONDITIONS?

414
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:06,083
THIS GUY CAN'T BE FOR REAL!

415
00:25:09,333 --> 00:25:11,458
WHAT KIND OF DEMON
AM I UP AGAINST?

